---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of use | Académie Évolution"
  description="Terms of use for Académie Évolution services."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="relative z-20 border-0">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <span class="tag anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.2s">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mt-4 anim-slide-l" style="--delay:.35s">Terms of use</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-3 anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.5s">Last updated: March 17, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance</h2>
          <p>By accessing the site, mobile app, or any Académie Évolution service, you accept these terms. If you disagree, please do not use our services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.15s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Services</h2>
          <p>We offer online fitness coaching, personalized training, nutrition guidance, and a tracking app. Services support general wellness and do not replace medical advice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Accounts</h2>
          <p>Some features require an account. You are responsible for your credentials and activity on your account. Registration information must be accurate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.25s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Subscriptions &amp; payments</h2>
          <p>Coaching subscriptions may be billed monthly. You may cancel anytime via the app or support. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. Refunds are handled case by case.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Health disclaimer</h2>
          <p>We are not a medical provider. Consult a health professional before starting an exercise program. You acknowledge risks of physical activity and participate voluntarily.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.35s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>Platform content (workouts, videos, text, visuals) is protected. Reproduction or derivative works without written permission are prohibited.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.4s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>To the extent permitted by law, we are not liable for indirect or consequential damages from use of our services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.45s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
          <p><a href="mailto:info@academieevolution.com" class="underline hover:text-white transition">info@academieevolution.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
